\c 4
\s Anoratidzwa Mwari ari pachigaro cheushe kudenga
\p
\v 1 Shure kweizvi ndakaona, zvino tarira, mukova wakazaruka kudenga, nenzwi rekutanga randakanzwa \add rakaita\add* serehwamanda richitaura neni, richiti: Kwira pano, ndigokuratidza zvinhu zvinofanira kuitika shure kweizvi.
\v 2 Zvino pakarepo ndakava muMweya; zvino tarira, chigaro cheushe chakagadzwa kudenga, nepamusoro pechigaro cheushe \add umwe\add* agere.
\v 3 Iye waiva    agere pakuonekwa waiva    akafanana nebwe rejasipisi* nesadhio*; nemurarabungu wakakomberedza chigaro cheushe waitaridzika sebwe reemaradhi*.
\v 4 Zvino zvigaro zveushe makumi maviri nezvina zvaiva    zvakakomberedza chigaro cheushe; nepazvigaro zveushe ndakaona vakuru makumi maviri nevana vagere, vakapfeka nguvo chena, uye vaiva    vane korona dzegoridhe pamisoro yavo.
\v 5 Nepachigaro cheushe pakabuda mheni nekutinhira nemanzwi; nemwenje minomwe yemoto ichipfuta pamberi pechigaro cheushe, iri Mweya minomwe yaMwari.
\v 6 Zvino pamberi pechigaro cheushe paiva    \add pane\add* gungwa regirazi, rakafanana nekrisitaro*. Nepakati pechigaro cheushe nepakapoteredza chigaro cheushe \add pane\add* zvisikwa zvina zvipenyu zvizere nemeso mberi neshure.
\v 7 Zvino chisikwa chipenyu chekutanga chaiva    chakafanana neshumba, uye chisikwa chipenyu chechipiri chakafanana nemhuru, nechisikwa chipenyu chechitatu chaiva    chine chiso semunhu, nechisikwa chipenyu chechina chaiva    chakafanana negondo rinobhururuka.
\v 8 Nezvisikwa zvipenyu \add izvi\add* chimwe nechimwe chaiva    chine mapapiro matanhatu mativi ese, nemukati zvaiva    zvizere nemeso; uye hazvizorori masikati neusiku, zvichiti: Mutsvene, mutsvene, mutsvene, Ishe Mwari, Wemasimbaose, waiva    aripo, uye aripo, neachazouya.
\v 9 Zvino apo zvisikwa zvipenyu izvi pazvaimupa kubwinya nerukudzo nekuvongwa iye anogara pachigaro cheushe, iye anorarama kusvika  rinhi narinhi,
\v 10 vakuru makumi maviri nevana vakazviwisira pasi pamberi peagere pachigaro cheushe ndokumunamata iye anorarama kusvika  rinhi narinhi, uye vachikandira korona dzavo pamberi pechigaro cheushe, vachiti:
\v 11 Makafanira, Ishe, kugamuchira kubwinya, nerukudzo, nesimba; nokuti ndimwi makasika zvinhu zvese, uye nekuda kwechido chenyu zviripo uye zvakasikwa.